replies.body:
First off you call them kids but you don't know their story and how about I share my story with you and maybe you can understand why you get very toxic players, now I'm only toxic in some games and not all of them. now ill explain my story and why I get toxic at some times This is true none of this is made up! Last year I turned 16 and my mum decided to kick me out of the house shortly after that one of my best friends died I was stressed enough with trying to find a flat I even went homeless a few days so this year the start of the year wasn't too bad I got myself a mate to live with and school was going fine. I started getting bullied in school constantly by the same group of people you could say just tell the teachers well that's the thing I told the deputy principle and my school Councillor and they didn't do much other than tell them off but heres the thing too when they got told off then they would get their friends to pick on me and I'd get so enraged and I'd want to kill them sometimes and if id ever react for some reason id end up in more trouble than them I stopped going to school and started failing the year and I got expelled for not going to school anymore. I even went to see a psychiatrist and he told me I had severe depression I even have a letter from him to prove it so. I play league every night which I find a very fun game to spent time with my friends and some games I just can't help but get angry and toxic because of what happened to me and I try honestly I do try but some games I can't help it now I'm not here to brag about my life story but I'm just here to tell you there is a reason behind every players toxicity sure you have no right to be toxic I can definitely agree with you, but you need to keep in mind that no one is toxic because they find it fun being so. and yes players do get banned when they get toxic I've been banned so I can't play the game anymore.

All I'm trying to say is you shouldn't be hurt by toxic players all very much you have no idea what in the world they are going through, sorry to have to explain my story I really didn't want to I just want to get the community to know that yes you have no excuse for being toxic but they shouldn't be getting too upset over toxic players and they shouldn't take it to heart when they get angry at you.

Peace {{champion:43}}
